<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV51">
<l>malaikoṇṭu mattā varavāṟ cuḻaṟṟiya māyappirā</l>
<l>ṉalaikaṇṭu koṇṭa vamutaṅkoḷ ḷātu kaṭalparatar</l>
<l>vilaikoṇṭu tantacaṅ kamivai vērit tuḻāytuṇaiyāt</l>
<l>tulaikoṇṭu tāyaṅ kiḷarntukoḷ vāṉot taḻaikkiṉṟatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The ocean, not taking [back] the amṛta that was taken, after seeing [it] in the waves,</l>
<l>by the cunning lord who churned, taking with the snake, the mountain as a churning stick,</l>
<l>it summons [me] as if to take [my] wealth in rising, taking [it] away,</l>
<l>with the sweet Tulsi for a companion, these bangles given for a price by the fishermen.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
